                <p>I am instructed to express the gratification of my government that by this
                    exchange of notes confirmation and validity are given to the agreement reached
                    by the commissioners, thus completing the award of the London tribunal under the
                    convention of January 24, 1903, as to the above-described part of the Alaska
                    boundary.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
